The date macro will display the current date and time:
{{{
<<today>>
}}}
Displays as:
<<today>>

This macro accepts one parameter - a date format. Such as:
{{{
<<today DD/MM/YYYY>>
}}}
Displays as:
<<today DD/MM/YYYY>>
Read more about [[Date Formats]]